
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "ProtectiveServices";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<!-- ***** Breadcumb Area Start ***** -->
<div class="mosh-breadcumb-area" style="background-image: url(../../wwwroot/img/core-img/executive.png);">
    <div class="container h-100">
        <div class="row h-100 align-items-center">
            <div class="col-12">
                <div class="bradcumbContent">
                    <h2>Protective Services</h2>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<!-- ***** Breadcumb Area End ***** -->
<!-- ***** Services Area Start ***** -->
<div class="container" style="padding-bottom:100px">
    <div class="align-items-center" style="padding-top:50px">
        <div class="col-md-12" style="text-align:justify">
            <p style="text-align:justify">
                Why should companies or businesses consider hiring VIP protection? 
                <br />For instance, if a person is going to be spending time in a “high-risk” area where criminal activity is well-known, then he or she would do well to be accompanied by an armed off duty or retired police officer. The more time spent in and among the public, where anyone or everyone has access to a person with money or fame, the more likely they’ll benefit from having VIP protection at their side.
            </p>
            <p> <b>We at NSS ensure our clients security anywhere around the globe.</b></p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <p style="text-align:justify">
                NSS provides protective services as a risk mitigation service to its clients taken to ensure the safety of VIPs or other individuals who may be exposed to elevated personal risk because of their employment, celebrity status, wealth, associations or geographical location.
            </p>
            <p style="text-align:justify">
                We provide protective service to both Corporate and Personal Sectors.
                <ul>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <ul>
                                <li>Close Protection Services</li>
                                <li>Specialist Security Services</li>
                                <li>Residential Protection</li>
                                <li>Valuables & Asset Escort & Delivery</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <ul>
                                <li>Child & Adult Recovery</li>
                                <li>Special Event Security</li>
                                <li>Halls and walls in the hotel</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </ul>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<!-- ***** Services Area End ***** -->
<!-- ***** CTA Area Start ***** -->
